description: Back on market due to buyer financing! Their loss is your gain!! New price!! Do you want outdoor space and 4 full sized bedrooms + dedicated office space in the city? Over those long commutes? This is your home! Step through the front door of this gracious single family home located in South Boston w/11 foot ceilings- flooded w/light! Open concept living room w/gas fireplace, flows into the dining room & kitchen. Half bath for guests, along w/deck for grilling & access to the low maintenance yard w/ patio pavers give you amazing entertaining spaces. Finished lower level has huge family room w/ 8ft ceilings, lots of storage space too! Primary bedroom has room for a king, oversized shower, separate toilet room, laundry, large walk-in & a separate shoe closet! 3 decks-including a roof deck + fenced paver patio + garage parking make this a true home in the city you won't outgrow.
